==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Suctoria
<hw>Suc*to"ri*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Suction</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An order of
Infusoria having the body armed with somewhat stiff, tubular processes
which they use as suckers in obtaining their food. They are usually
stalked.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Same as <er>Rhizocephala</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suctorial</ent>⟦br⟧
